item.description:

Good to know hes quite the comedian though.
[/quote]
you i agree on and no i wont get with her or have sex with her she is already dead now[/quote]

sorry for ur loss. if with that statement u are saying she committed the act. Wish i would have got on here yesterday. I would have told u to go to the police about it. so she could get help if u knew she was that serious. talking from experience(1.4+ years of depression), she needed help to realize, the big picture of life, the future, that this moment is just a moment and will seen pass. In my state of depression i lost all interest in life, and really didnt care about much. I was looking for something to give me purpose. I feel like im out of depression now but idk if its temporary or not. the depression started more than 2 years ago and i had like one thought in my mind keeping me from committing that act, then I started dating a girl while i was dating her, my depression seemed to be gone but after she left me i was in deep depression(lied in bed for days at a time when i did get up i lied around with little interest in anything, and i thought about suicide a lot.) for months then it got a little better but still in depression just not as deep. I think whats bringing me out of depression atm is this girl at my college has been flirting with me, so my spirits are up. the reason i was depressed b/c i felt worthless, thinking im the most boring person in the world, Im so different, no one would want to be around me, feeling stupid even though everyone always says im smart. just tons of self-esteem issues that i needed help with, and there were no environmentally factors that would have caused these issues; I just came up with them from examining the world and my life and everything. Also seeing how horrible the world is and how i am pretty powerless to change things also were a factor.
